alluxio.collections

Class UniqueFieldIndex<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.collections.UniqueFieldIndex<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of objects in this IndexedSet
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FieldIndex<T>, Iterable<T>

    @ThreadSafe
public class UniqueFieldIndex<T>
extends Object
implements FieldIndex<T>
    A class representing a unique index. A unique index is an index where each index value only maps to one object.
